com.opengamma.strata.pricer.calibration

Class ImmutableRatesProviderGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.pricer.calibration.ImmutableRatesProviderGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RatesProviderGenerator

    public class ImmutableRatesProviderGenerator
extends Object
implements RatesProviderGenerator
    Generates a rates provider based on an existing provider.

    This takes a base ImmutableRatesProvider and list of curve definitions to generate a child provider.
